PC PC_Lasbscs@Doas
process Doas@OpDoas
atom :'a'
atom :'b'
atom :'c'
atom :'nil'
operator OpDoas.Choice
operator OpDobs.Choice
operator OpDocs.Choice
process Dobs@OpDobs
process Docs@OpDocs
op_connector OpDoas->a
op_connector OpDoas->Dobs
after a->Doas
after b->Dobs
after c->Docs
op_connector OpDobs->b
op_connector OpDobs->Docs
op_connector OpDocs->c
op_connector OpDocs->nil
